room_title: Escape room "The Spell" by Talon Falls Escape in Paducah
review: I played the new game The Spell and I have to tell you it was absolutely amazing. I would definitely recommend playing this game. The way that the puzzles and clues are set up make it the best one by far in my opinion. I don't want to give anything away, but I will definitely be playing it again.
